Package: HCSQC
Title: Quality Control Workflow for High Content Screening
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('CEDRIC', 'HASSEN-KHODJA', email = 'cedric.hassen-khodja@mri.cnrs.fr', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: Purpose multiple measures of control quality to validate a HCS project. 
  The workflow calculates a coefficient of variation (CV), a Z-Prime factors (Z') 
  and a Strictly standardized mean difference (SSMD) for all selected positive or negative controls.
